程序包 moralScore

类 Volunteer

java.lang.Object
moralScore.Volunteer
所有已实现的接口:
Serializable
public class Volunteer extends Object implements Serializable
The Volunteer class represents a volunteer activity. It stores information about the volunteer's name, time, semester, credit, hours, rank, and verification status.
